<section id="metodo" class="reveal py-section relative">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center max-w-800 mx-auto mb-4">
            <p class="text-uppercase">MÉTODO ALGORITMIA</p>
            <h2 class="text-h2 mb-2">Cómo escalamos tu negocio</h2>
            <p class="text-lg">
                No improvisamos. <strong>No prometemos lo que no se puede cumplir.</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-wrapper">
            <div class="timeline-line"></div>

            <div class="timeline-item reveal">
                <div class="timeline-marker">1</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-icon"><i class="ph ph-magnifying-glass"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-h3 mb-2">01. Diagnóstico Estratégico</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        <strong>Analizamos tu negocio, métricas y mercado a fondo.</strong> 
                        Definimos objetivos claros y rentables contigo. 
                        Entendemos antes de ejecutar.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item reveal">
                <div class="timeline-marker">2</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-icon"><i class="ph ph-clipboard-text"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-h3 mb-2">02. Evaluación de Viabilidad</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        <strong>Evaluamos si tu objetivo es alcanzable hoy.</strong> 
                        Identificamos riesgos y ajustes necesarios. 
                        Si no es viable, proponemos alternativas.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item reveal">
                <div class="timeline-marker">3</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-icon"><i class="ph ph-strategy"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-h3 mb-2">03. Plan de Acción & Propuesta</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        <strong>Diseñamos una estrategia clara con acciones concretas.</strong> 
                        Definimos inversión, plazos y expectativas. 
                        Sin letra chica ni promesas vacías.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item reveal">
                <div class="timeline-marker">4</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-icon"><i class="ph ph-rocket-launch"></i></div>
                    <h3 class="text-h3 mb-2">04. Ejecución y Escalado</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        Implementamos campañas y activos digitales rentables. 
                        Iteramos basándonos en datos reales. 
                        <strong>Trabajamos contigo enfocados en tu crecimiento.</strong>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="guarantee-block reveal text-center max-w-800 mx-auto mt-8">
            <i class="ph ph-seal-check" style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--color-black); margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
            <h3 class="text-h3 mb-2">Garantía de Resultados</h3>
            <p class="text-h4">
                Si no alcanzamos el objetivo, <strong class="text-highlight-temp">te devolvemos el dinero.</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .timeline-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0rem 0;
    }

    .timeline-line {
        position: absolute;
        left: 20px;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--border-light), transparent);
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .timeline-item {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        position: relative;
        align-items: center;
        transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
        
        /* Reveal Logic */
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
    }

    .timeline-item.visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* Hover Spotlight Effect - Only triggers when hovering an item */
    .timeline-wrapper:has(.timeline-item:hover) .timeline-item {
        opacity: 0.4;
    }
    
    .timeline-wrapper .timeline-item:hover {
        opacity: 1;
        filter: blur(0);
        transform: scale(1.02);
        z-index: 10;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        background: var(--bg-body);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        z-index: 10; /* Ensure it's above the line */
        position: relative;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px var(--bg-body);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .timeline-item:hover .timeline-marker {
        background: var(--color-black);
        color: var(--color-white);
        border-color: var(--color-black);
    }

    .timeline-content {
        background: var(--bg-surface);
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
        width: 100%;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .timeline-item:hover .timeline-content {
        background: var(--color-white);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        border-color: var(--border-light);
    }

    .timeline-icon {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .timeline-line { left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
        .timeline-item { width: 50%; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; }
        .timeline-marker { width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) {
            margin-left: 0;
            margin-right: auto;
            padding-right: 3rem;
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-marker { position: absolute; right: -25px; top: 0; }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: 0;
            padding-left: 3rem;
        }
        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-marker { position: absolute; left: -25px; top: 0; }
    }
</style>
